/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The vantage point is high, providing a bird's eye view of the urban landscape. The street, teeming with life, stretches out below, lined with a variety of buildings and trees that add a touch of green to the concrete jungle. Cars and buses are scattered along the road, hinting at the rhythm of city life. Overhead, power lines crisscross against the backdrop of a clear blue sky, a common sight in many urban areas. The image is slightly distorted due to the fisheye lens effect, adding a unique perspective to the scene.
